These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, freelancer
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, indonesian
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, ship
1. the freelancer is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the photographer is on the right of the freelancer##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | water      | cola    |
| Job           | freelancer | photographer |
| Nationality   | turkish       | indonesian  |
| Transport     | car      | ship     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, spinach
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
2 different pets are kept: dog, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, bike
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | spinach | potato |
| Music-Genre   | classical       | country         |
| Pet           | hamster     | dog         |
| Transport     | bike    | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, manager
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, pop
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | woodworking          | filmmaking |
| Job           | manager | dancer     |
| Music-Genre   | trance            | pop         |
| Transport     | train         | motorbike   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, fantasy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, house
2 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse
1. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | house |
| Pet           | ferret | mouse    |

