.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, garlic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person eating cabbage is the fan of reggae##1
3. the fan of reggae is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | juice     | 7up |
| Food          | garlic   | cabbage |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | reggae     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | bike     |

 